data.description: Beautiful downstairs unit condo located in the well-maintained Gated community of Keys Condominiums! Just a few minutes away from the Las Vegas Strip, New MLB Stadium and Allegiant Stadium!  This 1 bedroom 1 bath condo features a nice kitchen with granite countertops, all appliances included, and a pantry and dining area. Cozy patio with solar screens. Tile flooring throughout. Great community amenities with pool/spa, clubhouse, exercise room,  Close proximity to schools, shopping, dining and more! All appliances included! Come see this unit today!
